annotationA: Uncharacterized protein, isoform A; Damaged DNA binding. It is involved in the biological process described with: mRNA splicing, via spliceosome; mitotic spindle organization; neurogenesis
annotationB: Probable U2 small nuclear ribonucleoprotein A; U2A is a protein component of the U2 snRNP. The U2 snRNP combines with other snRNPs on the pre-mRNA to assemble a spliceosome
